## Constitution Check (Critical)

**Before any scaffolding or execution:**

```
docs/constitution/
├── PRODUCT.md        # Must exist
├── TECH.md           # Must exist
└── GOVERNANCE.md     # Must exist
```

**If any are missing or empty:** STOP. Request from Human Lead.

